                            {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "immobilized",
                                "alt": "immobilized",
                                "game-obj": "Conditions",
                                "aonid": 81
                            }
                        ],
                        "text": "If the giant chameleon hits a creature with a tongue Strike, that creature becomes grabbed by the giant chameleon. The target isn't immobilized, but it can't move beyond the reach of the giant chameleon's tongue. A creature can sever the tongue with a Strike against AC 15 that deals at least 4 slashing damage. Though this doesn't deal any damage to the giant chameleon, it prevents it from using its tongue Strike until it regrows its tongue, which takes a week."
